data.description: Escape to a new paradise just minutes away from the Matanzas River & Crescent Beach. This home overlooks a pond that has phenomenal sunset views off of your back patio where you sit relaxing with a cold beverage. The home's features include: upon your entry you walk thru the foyer and into the open concept living area; a spacious family room greets you, that is perfect for those lazy days in front of the TV or entertaining guests for a get together; large combo dining area off the FR is perfect to have your meals; huge center island in the kitchen with slide up bar seating plus lots of cabinet space and a walk-in pantry for all your storage needs; home offers a split bedroom pattern for those people that enjoy privacy from their guests; oversized master suite with plenty of room for a king size bed, dresser, armoire and side tables with room to spare; walk-in closet plus his & her vanity sinks in the master bath; inside laundry; ring security cameras; mult fruit trees and so much more.
